  2022,"10",/general-conference/2022/10/14renlund,Elder Dale G. Renlund,44,"See Thomas S. Monson, “Whom Shall I Marry?,”New Era, Oct. 2004, 4."
  2022,"10",/general-conference/2022/10/14renlund,Elder Dale G. Renlund,45,"SeeDoctrine and Covenants 59:9–16."
