  2022,"10",/general-conference/2022/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,17,"We have released Elders Weatherford T. Clayton, LeGrand R. Curtis Jr., Randy D. Funk, Christoffel Golden, Walter F. González, Larry S. Kacher, Lynn G. Robbins, and Joseph W. Sitati as General Authority Seventies and grant them emeritus status."
  2022,"10",/general-conference/2022/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,18,Those who wish to express gratitude to these brethren and to their wives and families for their years of dedicated service may do so by the uplifted hand.
  2022,"10",/general-conference/2022/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,19,We also note with appreciation the Area Seventies who have completed their service during this past year and whose names can be found on newsroom.ChurchofJesusChrist.org.
