  2022,"10",/general-conference/2022/10/35andersen,Elder Neil L. Andersen,58,"Elder David B. Haight said:"
  2022,"10",/general-conference/2022/10/35andersen,Elder Neil L. Andersen,59,"“It is true that some have actually seen the Savior, but when one consults the dictionary, he learns that there are many other meanings of the wordsee, such as coming to know Him, discerning Him, recognizing Him and His work, perceiving His importance, or coming to understand Him."
  2022,"10",/general-conference/2022/10/35andersen,Elder Neil L. Andersen,60,"“Such heavenly enlightenment and blessings are available to each of us” (“Temples and Work Therein,”Ensign, Nov. 1990, 61)."
