  2022,"10",/general-conference/2022/10/35andersen,Elder Neil L. Andersen,66,"Dallin H. Oaks, “Going Forward in the Second Century” (Brigham Young University devotional, Sept. 13, 2022), speeches.byu.edu. President Oaks credited the phrase “dare to be different” to a recent article in theDeseret Magazineby Elder Clark G. Gilbert, the Church Educational System Commissioner, on preserving religious identity in higher education (see “Dare to Be Different,”Deseret Magazine, Sept. 2022, deseret.com)."
  2022,"10",/general-conference/2022/10/35andersen,Elder Neil L. Andersen,67,"If you would like to learn from others who commented on how they have been different from the world, you can read their comments on Facebook (see Neil L. Andersen, Facebook, Aug. 18, 2022, facebook.com/neill.andersen) or Instagram (see Neil L. Andersen, Instagram, Aug. 18, 2022, instagram.com/neillandersen)."
