  2022,"10",/general-conference/2022/10/53schmitt,Elder Jonathan S. Schmitt,57,"In a recent worldwide devotional for young adults, Sister Wendy Nelson posed a question that she said could change lives, increase confidence and decrease anxiety, motivate, increase gratitude and decrease stress, help resist temptation, and bring joy, comfort, love, and peace. That question was “What would a holy young adult do?” She then encouraged application of this question in just one situation each day for three successive days. See “One Question That Can Change Your Life” (worldwide devotional for young adults, May 15, 2022), broadcasts.ChurchofJesusChrist.org."
